        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Safeguarding American Personal Information and Investment Act or the Safeguarding American PII Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Defense Production Act of 1950 to require national security reviews by the Committee on Foreign Investment to take into account whether the merger, acquisition, or takeover could expose the personally identifiable information of U.S. persons in a manner that threatens national security.</p>]]></text>
